[ti:Row Row Row Your Boat]
[ar:Children's Nursery Rhyme]
[al:Little English Star]

[00:03.00]Row, row, row your boat
[00:05.00]Gently down the stream
[00:08.00]Merrily, merrily, merrily, merrily
[00:09.50]Life is but a dream
[00:12.00]Row, row, row your boat
[00:12.50]Gently down the brook
[00:15.35]If you see a crocodile
[00:17.00]Don't forget to shout!
